      "content": "Here is a draft paragraph for your guide: \"During the initial transition period tomorrow morning, while our new system offers enhanced processing speeds, we want to proactively inform you that the nuances of deeply personalized travel itineraries may feel slightly different as we optimize the integration. Our team remains committed to providing the highest level of bespoke service, and we appreciate your patience as we fine-tune this advanced capability to meet your luxury expectations.\" This phrasing acknowledges the change while assuring them of continued high-quality care.",
